<span class="token code"><span class="token punctuation">\`\`\`</span>
<span class="token code-block">4
YaoLin 87 82 Y N 0
ChenRuiyi 88 78 N Y 1
LiXin 92 88 N N 0
ZhangQin 83 87 Y N 1</span>
<span class="token punctuation">\`\`\`</span></span>

